{"tid":865062,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 8大陸換mon（疑似騙案）","createTime":"2018-10-16T16:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T01:07:25.000Z","uid":186182,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"24f0d1f991c3499b6f92239807835943ca93c785","tid":865062,"uid":186182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:37:55.000Z","msg":"今日返撚左大陸換mon（玻璃mon 爆左有一條裂痕），佢收我$150人仔<br />\n即場睇住個師傅換搞左10分鐘，換好個顯示好似好似好正常咁。<br />\n<br />\n換完想囉返舊裂左個塊mon同癡住係底個塊金屬片，<br />\n點知個蛇頭鼠目肥仔師傅話唔得。佢話如果係咁唔係收$150，但佢換前無同我講換好要收我舊個塊。<br />\n<br />\n又話如果唔換塊鐵片只換mon 等多一個鐘同埋要囉去第到先有機器分開到塊mon同金屬片。叫我寫野上去塊金屬做record就唔怕佢換野。<br />\n<br />\n咁我緊係老死唔同意要佢換返舊的還原。佢仲想收返我$30人仔手工費，我緊係2話不說睇實佢換返曬所有野就走人。<br />\n<br />\n有無iphone維修專家<br />\n想問佢係唔係想出估惑偷我塊原廠金屬？<br />\n有無人有類似經驗選左比左舊個塊佢？有無中伏？"},{"pid":"8cba207366ad7ef8cb2c0497c9a468ce77f45315","tid":865062,"uid":1085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:46:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd3fd66056f1ad5e731097adb08565a7a625cc35","tid":865062,"uid":182286,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:46:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76c79fe298326d64e6eac2079fd94e7c11d71fe1","tid":865062,"uid":47128,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T16:49:47.000Z","msg":"爆左玻璃嘅mon其實可以分離返出黎<br />\n有回收價值"},{"pid":"7aa83922cc3b32199afb69d205341f122fb28f6a","tid":865062,"uid":147489,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T18:08:33.000Z","msg":"佢已經拎左你入面d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0cb34854c5a3e8377834ae43f2853920865b94","tid":865062,"uid":4917,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T18:10:47.000Z","msg":"亂咁出去搵人整已經夠戇鳩<br />\n仲要支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2faf81fefaf9d24342427d2ba48cbd93a596c1e","tid":865062,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T18:19:38.000Z","msg":"返大陸就預咗啦"},{"pid":"221204a06c81700db0636eaed218ce657a14ce3f","tid":865062,"uid":167573,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ec0cb34854c5a3e8377834ae43f2853920865b94","tid":865062,"uid":4917,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T18:10:47.000Z","msg":"亂咁出去搵人整已經夠戇鳩<br />\n仲要支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T18:21:39.000Z","msg":"你叻囉. 返蘋果整囉."},{"pid":"8cd72cfd0563931f541996d7b7ab4087811999fd","tid":865062,"uid":53620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T18:21:41.000Z","msg":"其實香港都係咁做 塊金屬嘢係液晶最少3-400<br />\n淨係換玻璃先會咁平"},{"pid":"8bc6c7c7491ce887be79ba5acbdbcc1a7c41b821","tid":865062,"uid":4917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"221204a06c81700db0636eaed218ce657a14ce3f","tid":865062,"uid":167573,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ec0cb34854c5a3e8377834ae43f2853920865b94","tid":865062,"uid":4917,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T18:10:47.000Z","msg":"亂咁出去搵人整已經夠戇鳩<br />\n仲要支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T18:21:39.000Z","msg":"你叻囉. 返蘋果整囉."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T00:21:26.000Z","msg":"梗係返蘋果整啦<br />\n用個屎忽諗下都知，你用埋原廠mon去換人地塊山寨mon<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df5119991c9d05f80c470e24ae0683c82bfd1f3","tid":865062,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T00:24:44.000Z","msg":"攞嚟賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b12149060ef83e73a5b5de4f33e1c7e81d13f12","tid":865062,"uid":67089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T00:25:45.000Z","msg":"成個顯示換左?出面冇原廠顯示賣，最多得拆機moon,而且好貴。百幾蚊一係山寨moon,一係換玻璃"},{"pid":"13029c635c3844cedaf7881ebf73146c9c13a86f","tid":865062,"uid":34213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T00:36:45.000Z","msg":"如果淨係裂玻璃，塊玻璃就唔值錢嘅<br />\n<br />\n但會話壞埋下面個兩層野，咁佢回收左自己加塊玻璃就可以當原廠螢幕whole assembly賣囉<br />\n<br />\n所以要收返下面金屬個舊嘢，因為佢哋就係靠呢舊嘢將來再加塊玻璃再賣出去"},{"pid":"d0a9c89dc3292330b114ad27c90f119a133f5c14","tid":865062,"uid":80650,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T01:04:44.000Z","msg":"佢想回收你個舊芒panel再用<br />\n換過塊新玻璃<br />\n其實你返華強北都只有呢三種芒:<br />\n拆機屏，即係原裝機拆出黎既舊芒<br />\n後壓屏，即係換過玻璃，但用原廠屏panel既芒<br />\n國產屏，即係山寨芒<br />\n<br />\nip8 $150一個芒，仲要賺你人工，用山寨芒都未必得<br />\n反而佢幫你換個後壓屏，之後收你舊芒條屍<br />\n佢既成本就只係一塊玻璃，咁就合理好多"},{"pid":"85a0da381938bb64aefa39daeb4d8779f0356014","tid":865062,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T01:07:25.000Z","msg":"返大陸唔幫你降做iphone7咪算好囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}